CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: TXO Energy Partners, L.P. focuses on the acquisition, development, optimization and exploitation of conventional oil, natural gas, and natural gas liquid reserves in North America. Its acreage positions are concentrated in the Permian Basin of West Texas and New Mexico and the San Juan Basin of New Mexico and Colorado. The company was formerly known as MorningStar Partners, L.P. and changed its name to TXO Energy Partners, L.P. in January 2023. TXO Energy Partners, L.P. was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Fort Worth, Texas.
